title: A590 reopened after 3 car collision
text:
Road traffic collision A590 Credit: ITV Border Police were called today to reports of a three vehicle collision on the A590 close to Greenodd Ulverston.
The vehicles below were involved in the collision:
- A Red Skoda Fabia, driven by a 54 year old female from Lancashire - A grey Renault Scenic, driven by a 43 year old woman from Ulverston - A Silver Vauxhall driven by a 48 year old woman from Ulverston All three drivers received treatment for minor injuries at the scene.
The road was closed for a time following the collision to allow police investigation and for recovery of vehicles.
